# Employee Attrition Analysis Dashboard (Power BI)

This Power BI project analyzes employee attrition trends to help HR teams understand key factors behind employee turnover.

## Objective
To create an interactive Power BI dashboard that shows:
- Total employees
- Attrition count and rate
- Insights by age, gender, salary, education, job role, and years at company

## Tools Used
- Power BI Desktop
- DAX
- Excel (for data source)

## Dashboard Features
- KPI Cards for overall numbers
- Bar and pie charts for attrition breakdowns
- Slicers for department-wise filtering
- Visualizations for age, education, gender, and salary insights

## Files Included
- `AttritionDashboard.pbix` – Power BI file
- `Screenshots/` – Folder with dashboard images
- `Portfolio.pdf` – Project summary document

## Conclusion
This dashboard helps HR professionals make data-driven decisions to reduce employee attrition and improve retention.

